lead_paragraph: Valencia coach Gary Neville angrily brushed off questions about his future ahead of his struggling team's visit to La Liga leaders Barcelona in the King's Cup semi-finals on Wednesday.

headline.print_headline: Tetchy Neville Seeks Nou Camp Inspiration for Valencia
